description:
One Week by Barenaked Ladies
Clips from Good Omens
I own nothing.
______________
This was supposed to become a more humorous edit than it ended up being - I realised about halfway through that I couldn't make it into the thing I originally wanted it to be (one of those videos highlighting lots of the funny quotes of the show) because the song worked too well for that. It's still upbeat enough for my liking, though. I'll still try to make that other kind of edit at some point. Enjoy this one in the meantime!
